title: First Look: 2025 LOOK E-765 Gravel and E-765 Road eBikes
content:
The LOOK E-765 Gravel and Road eBikes are lighter than their predecessors, with more power, increased range, and clearance for bigger tires.

Read the full article at First Look: 2025 LOOK E-765 Gravel and E-765 Road eBikes on Velo.
